Sentencas: An anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) was fabricated using a porous composite of Sr2MgMoO6-delta (SMM) and Gd0.1Ce0.9O2-delta (GDC) for the anode support.
Titulo: Sr2MgMoO6-δ/Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 composite anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC)

Sentencas: The electrolyte consisted of a 20 mu m thick GDC layer, which was deposited by a combined screen-printing and sol-gel deposition processes.
Titulo: Sr2MgMoO6-δ/Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 composite anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC)

Sentencas: A porous (La0.6Sr0.4)(0.98) (Co0.2Fe0.8)O3-delta (LSCF) composition was used as the active cathode.
Titulo: Sr2MgMoO6-δ/Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 composite anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC)

Sentencas: Voltage-current-power (V-I-P) tests were completed on the cells in wet H-2, and the fuel cells displayed a maximum power density of 342 mW cm(-2) and 572 mW cm(-2) at 600 degrees C and 700 degrees C, respectively, without the use of any metal impregnate to enhance the electro-catalytic processes.
Titulo: Sr2MgMoO6-δ/Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 composite anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC)
